data.description: WHY WAIT TO BUILD?! Built in 2021, this home is located in the popular waterfront community of Gulf Cove on the Myakka River, very close to the community boat ramp with access to Charlotte Harbor and the Gulf of Mexico. The large, and unique open floor plan is perfect for entertaining with easy conversation between the Livingroom, Kitchen, and Dinette area.  Features include over 1,400 square feet of living space, a Solar Panel on the Roof that significantly reduces electricity costs, 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances, an interior laundry room, and 2-Car Garage.  Gulf Cove is a waterfront community that offers an OPTIONAL HOA for just $75 a year which allows access to amenities like a waterfront park/playground/barbeque/picnic area with many community events each year. Members of the HOA can also purchase a boat ramp decal for $75 to use the community boat ramp to launch your boat and enjoy a day out on the water.  Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity – schedule your showing today!
